HEADWORD: Moonshiner
<hw>Moon"shin`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A person engaged
in illicit distilling; -- so called because the work is largely done at
night.</def> <mark>[Cant, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

